    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Wash your<strong> leek[s] </strong>thoroughly to remove any grit from between the leaves then top, tail and slice into rounds</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
