            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based <strong>hob-safe</strong> <strong>oven-proof casserole dish </strong>with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced leek</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the dish</p><p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
