    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>to the dish with your <strong>tortiglioni</strong>,<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt  </strong>and 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[525ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Nestle the pasta into the water as much as you can, then give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1680606604861-x200.jpg",
