            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped basa</strong> to the dish and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min or until the pasta and basa are cooked through (your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily)</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p><p>Tip: Give everything a stir halfway through for evenly cooked pasta!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
