      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pasta is cooked, remove the dish from the oven and stir through your<strong> crème fraîche</strong> and<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>oven-baked creamy basa & leek tortiglioni</strong></p>",
